# RQ-53-20-03-151: NDT Inspection Schedule (C-Check)

## Requirement Statement
The BWB outer skin panels shall undergo ultrasonic NDT inspection at C-Check intervals (6,000 FH) to detect internal damage.

## Rationale
Detect delaminations, disbonds, and moisture ingress not visible externally.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Ultrasonic C-scan of high-risk areas
- Coverage: 100% of critical zones (doors, windows, frames)
- Acceptance criteria: No defects > 25mm diameter
- Inspection time budget: 8 man-hours per aircraft

## Compliance Status
NDT procedure in development

## Traceability
Parent: CS-25.571, AMC 25.571
